            Miles Capital is an investment advisory firm that provides a range of financial products and services. The firm serves various individual investors, institutions, municipalities, government agencies, retirement plans, corporations, foundations and endowments. It offers full-service banking solutions to businesses and consumers, as well as banking organizations. Miles Capital provides managed accounts and mutual funds. It also offers services that include portfolio management, investment portfolio modeling and analysis, liability management review and asset allocation consulting.
          






















