Capital Markets

Company Overview of Miles Capital, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Miles Capital, Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to insurance companies and other corporations, banks, corporate pension and profit-sharing plans, charitable institutions, foundations, endowments, municipalities and government agencies, registered mutual funds, private investment funds, trust programs, other U.S. institutions, and high net worth individuals. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm invests in public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe. For its equity investments, it invests in exchange-listed securities, exchange-traded funds, securities traded over-the-cou...
Miles Capital, Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to insurance companies and other corporations, banks, corporate pension and profit-sharing plans, charitable institutions, foundations, endowments, municipalities and government agencies, registered mutual funds, private investment funds, trust programs, other U.S. institutions, and high net worth individuals. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm invests in public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe. For its equity investments, it invests in exchange-listed securities, exchange-traded funds, securities traded over-the-counter, and ADRs. The firm primarily invests in stocks of small-cap and large-cap companies. For its fixed income investments, the firm invests in debt securities; commercial paper; municipal securities; investment company securities, United States Government securities, bank deposits, and other securities, including convertible bonds, preferred stocks. For its alternative investments, it invests in private equity hedge funds, real estate, and commodities, or commercial mortgage loans. The firm employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. Miles Capital, Inc. was founded in 1982 and is based in West Des Moines, Iowa.
Detailed Description


